        "question_rTVREe": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "default_open": false,
            "title": "How do your Bib Tights fit?",
            "content": "<p>Our tights fit true to size. We have a robust and detailed size chart on the product page to help you get dialed in. If you're in between sizes, we recommend sizing down because a more fitted bottom gives you the best chance at comfort.</p>",
